sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: TC_013_CSMS: Hard Reset (Table 133, p.119)
    Note over CP,CS: Section 3.5.1 - Core Profile - Resetting Happy Flow

    CS->>CP: Reset.req (type = Hard)
    CP-->>CS: Reset.conf (status = Accepted)

    Note over CP: Charge Point performs hard reset and reboots

    CP->>CS: BootNotification.req
    CS-->>CP: BootNotification.conf (status = Accepted)

    loop For each connector (including connectorId=0)
        CP->>CS: StatusNotification.req (status = Available)
        CS-->>CP: StatusNotification.conf
    end
